Font::TTFMetrics version 0.01
============================

Font::TTFMetrics is a fast, easy-to-use parser for true-type font (TTF) file. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

Nothing special.

